text:
Yaad hai second semester me mila tha tumse , tab se lekr kafi courses, labs aur assignment kiye hai sath me. ESO207 ka wo extra assignment hamesha yaad rahega jisme last minute debugging help ki thi. EE200 ka tutorial tere karan interesting ho jata tha and  last two years se to bas ispr hi discussion hota hai ki labs, courses ya power me kya ho rha.

Kafi interesting aur enjoy kiya hai sath me aur aage bhi aisa hi ho. Tum ek aache aur amazing friend ho, aage bhi chapte rahna. 
Cheers to the memories and mess table discussions.

Raat k wo long walks and discussion on electrical kyu nahi acha ğŸ˜›(ofc acha hai) miss karunga and treat bhi pending hai. At last tum kafi down to earth and motivated towards your career hoâ€¦. text:
Bhai tum sach me akarshan ho!
First year summer me mile the and yaad hai wo sg form filling k time baat kiya tha. I am very fortunate ki tere sath hi allocate hua aur orientationâ€™18 me Hall 13 subah subah easy ho gya. Tumne kafi change kiya my perspective about life at IITK. I remember ham even second year me sath jaate the Hall-13 and jo bhi issues thi baccho ki sath solve krte.
Tumse maine kafi kuch seekha and tera third year ka birthday kafi interesting tha. I remember ham kafi kuch discuss kiye about our IITK life, kya change krna chahiye and kya nahi, personal life and how CS k interview sahi nahi hue xD. Wo OAT ki treat me kafi mazze aaye the jo baccho ko diye the just after orientation.
Bhai tum one of the most awesome aur nicest person ho pure IITK batch me.  
Final year me utna discussion to nahi hua but hamesha aise hi rahna aur milte hai :) 
BBQ & hall-12 me chocolate dene k liye thanks aur aise hi financial tips dete raho. I know kaafi aage jaoge tum.
author: Shashank  Shailabh

text:
Yo groot (Chaapu)!
Bhai kha se hi start karu. First sem se hi sath me rahe phir wo TA101 k lab ho ya Antaragini EDM. Yaad hai second year me EDM sath gye the aur wo vent ground wali photos bhai kya epic thi. Kitne hi courses me sath me padhai kari hai aur kitne nightout kare library me. Tu group ka doubt solver tha first year se hi and even intern k tests me bhi.
Tere sath pubg nahi khela itna lekin bhai kya dedication hai pubg k videos ka ki jab bhi tere room pr aata tu ya to video dekh rha hota tha ya padhai. 
Yaad hai wo second year k december me project liya tha and kaise kaat diya tha hamne. Abhi tak hassi aati hai wo presentation k expression soch soch kr ğŸ˜‚
Yaad hai wo  BBQ me intern party k baad kya discussion hua tha ki kaise auto ka paisa diya jayeğŸ˜.
Iskon temple aur bithur ka cycling trip pr to kay memories bani thi specially wo songs ka.  
kuch bhi bolo chaapu ho tum bhai aur tujhe last sem me campus aana chahiye tha. 
Milte rahna aur aisi hi aur bhi cycling trips pr chalte hai :)
author: Shashank  Shailabh

text:

Bhai chaapu ho tum ye ab accept kr lena. TA202 me sath the tab se final days ki treat tak bahot mazze aaye. Yaad hai sabse pahle tere se bonding ta202 me night out krna se hui thi aur tune jo video dikhayi sabko wo dekh kr hi pata lg gya ki tum bade h****i  ho xD 
Prayas me kaam krne kafi sahi tha lekin tumne first sem me bahot fraud mara tha :( . Winter me wing me cricket khelna ho, akele luck ke jana ho, OAT me treat ho ya celebration ho prayas me sabme mazze aaye. 
Milte rahana aur aage bhi wo whatsapp group pr aise hi harkate krte rha, ğŸ˜›
